		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />My <a href="http://blargg.parodius.com/nes-tests/nes_instr_test.zip" class="postlink">nes_instr_test</a> should work. While it uses the PPU if available, it doesn't hang if it's not or if it doesn't work. It outputs all text to memory as well, so you can examine it even without a PPU. See the readme for full information.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
